  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are located in the Villa Flora, a newer building 50 metres away from the main hotel. They are elegantly furnished in typical Italian style with garden views. Facilities include air conditioning, satellite TV and free wifi. They can sleep up to two adults and are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are in the Villa Flora and enjoy sea views. They can sleep up to two adults and are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Gallery Rooms</strong> are on two levels in the Villa Flora with a spacious seating area on the ground floor and bedroom on the top floor. They have sea or village views and can sleep up to three adults. They are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> are located in the Timeo building, which is part of the main hotel. They have sumptuous furnishings and sea views. They accommodate up to two adults.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> sleep up to three people and are located in Villa Flora. They have a seating area and it’s possible to have rooms that interconnect for larger families. They are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are in the Timeo building and are finished in a Sicilian Baroque style with a balcony and sea views. They sleep up to three adults and are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
